k\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 15, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cau1665703006644.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cau1665703006644.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cau1665703006644.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cau1665703006644\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">$about \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"cau1665703006644___about_252071\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Returns information about the current Uniface installation, version, and platform.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"cau1665703006644__topic_d80237e1_d80238e1_d80239e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cau1665703006644__p_d80240e1_d80241e1_d80242e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$about</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cau1665703006644__topic_d52787e1_d52788e1_d52789e1_d52790e1_d52791e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d523844e66\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Information returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$about</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__1\">Property </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__3\">Example</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">tag</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__2\">Not used </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__3\">N/A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">update</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__2\">Not used </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__3\">N/A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">track</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__2\">Full Uniface version number, including the\n                        build identifier </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">10.3.01.007 (007 1027_1</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">date</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__2\">Build date </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">December 14, 2018</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">config</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__2\">Build configuration identifier </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1004_1</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">platform</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__2\">Platform compatibility code, such as W10, LU7,\n                        or RSG. For details, see <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://community.rocketsoftware.com/rocket-uniface-product-updates-108/uniface-product-availability-information-18191\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Platform Availability Matrix</a> in the Rocket\n                        Community Forum.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">W10</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">version</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__2\"> Uniface version number</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cau1665703006644__table_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">10.3.01</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cau1665703006644__topic_d52792e1_d52793e1_d52794e1_d52795e1_d52796e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d523844e221\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cau1665703006644__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cau1665703006644__topic_d52797e1_d52798e1_d52799e1_d52800e1_d52801e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d523844e230\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cau1665703006644__p_d80255e1_d80256e1_d80257e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$about</span> function returns an\n            associative list of properties and their values, which describe the current Uniface\n            installation. You can include this information in an About dialog, commonly available\n            from the Help menu of most applications.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cau1665703006644__section_hbc_zyq_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d523844e243\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$about</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following code displays an information dialog with the Uniface\n               version, build, and date.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cau1665703006644__pre_v5z_zyq_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail\nvariables\n string vVersion\n string vBuild\n string vBuildDate\nendvariables\ngetitem/id vVersion $about \"version\"\ngetitem/id vBuild $about \"config\"\ngetitem/id vBuildDate $about \"date\"\naskmess/info \"Uniface version: %%vVersion%%% (%%vBuild%%%) %%^Date: %%vBuildDate%%%\", \"OK\"\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"cau1665703006644__fig_w1879ab1b7b9b5b7_w1880ab1b7b9b5_w1881ab1b7b9_w1882ab1b7_w1883ab1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Information Returned by $about</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Information Returned by $about\" class=\"image\" id=\"cau1665703006644__image_w5z_zyq_zbc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/about.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526348\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526348\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$about Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 15, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $about Returns information about the current Uniface installation, version, and platform. $about Return Values Table 1. Information returned by $about Property Description Example tag Not used N/A update Not used N/A track Full Uniface version number, including the build identifier 10.3.01.007 (007 1027_1 date Build date December 14, 2018 config Build configuration identifier 1004_1 platform Platform compatibility code, such as W10, LU7, or RSG. For details, see Platform Availability Matrix in the Rocket Community Forum. W10 version Uniface version number 10.3.01 Use Allowed in all component types. Description The $about function returns an associative list of properties and their values, which describe the current Uniface installation. You can include this information in an About dialog, commonly available from the Help menu of most applications. Example: Using $about The following code displays an information dialog with the Uniface version, build, and date. trigger detail variables string vVersion string vBuild string vBuildDate endvariables getitem/id vVersion $about \"version\" getitem/id vBuild $about \"config\" getitem/id vBuildDate $about \"date\" askmess/info \"Uniface version: %%vVersion%%% (%%vBuild%%%) %%^Date: %%vBuildDate%%%\", \"OK\" end Copy Figure 1. Information Returned by $about Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}